flowchart TD
    Tick([Game loop tick]) --> State[Check current game state]
    State -->|ACTIVE_GAME| Spawn[Spawn enemies and bonuses]
    Spawn --> Move[Update enemy, bullet, and bonus positions]
    Move --> Collision[CollisionManager.checkCollisions()]
    Collision --> Difficulty[DifficultyManager.updateDifficulty()]
    Difficulty --> Cleanup[GameWorld.removeExpiredObjects()]
    Cleanup --> Stats[Update game stats and time]
    Stats --> UI[UiPort.updateScore/updateHealth/renderFrame()]
    UI --> Check[Check for player destruction]
    Check -->|destroyed| GameOver[Stop game and show Game Over]
    Check -->|alive| Loop[Continue next tick]
    State -->|not active| Idle[Skip updates until resume]
